-- BioMerieux Shares Slump After Company Cuts Sales Growth Outlook for 2010
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-22T07:11:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/biomerieux-shares-slump-after-company-cuts-sales-growth-outlook-for-2010.html

          
          
             BioMerieux SA shares declined after
the company cut its sales growth forecast for 2010.  
 The stock dropped as much as 9 percent and was down 8.8
percent at 81.81 euros at 9:09 a.m. in Paris. The company today
cut its full-year sales growth target to 6 percent from a
previous forecast of around 7 percent.  
          
          


  


        